data.description: Beautiful custom home nestled on 10.5 acres. In the country but 5 minutes from town. There is a 30 x 40 shop, a bonus room above garage. A 10 x 10 concrete  safe room inside the garage.  There is a creek running through the property that brings lots of wildlife.  Fenced back yard.
data.whatILove: Country living at its finest.  Peaceful,  and very quiet.  Lots of nature.  Room for horses or cattle. Room for atv rides. Cozy rock fireplace.  Such a spacious home for a family.  Lots of relaxing porches.
